// 导出配置
export const API_URL = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE_URL
export const API_PREFIX = import.meta.env.VITE_API_PREFIX
export const MEDIA_URL = import.meta.env.VITE_MEDIA_URL
export const SOCKET_URL = import.meta.env.VITE_SOCKET_URL

// 完整的API基础URL
export const API_BASE_URL = `${API_URL}${API_PREFIX}`

export default {
  API_URL,
  API_PREFIX,
  API_BASE_URL,
  MEDIA_URL,
  SOCKET_URL
}
